        {
            "title": "勝獅貨櫃發盈警 料去年純利跌最少47%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">勝獅貨櫃(00716)發盈警，預期2025年股東應佔綜合溢利不多於1800萬美元，較對上年度的3413.5萬美元跌起碼47.27%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：勝獅貨櫃官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/bplib_20230705-104215_source-web_00716.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：勝獅貨櫃官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/bplib_20230705-104215_source-web_00716.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：勝獅貨櫃官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該公司解釋，去年盈利倒退，主要因為整體行業面臨嚴峻挑戰，業務表現受到2024年集裝箱行業產量過剩所影響，導致乾集裝箱平均價格呈下降趨勢，並加劇了市場競爭壓力。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">此外，持續變化的美國關稅及貿易政策不斷加劇市場不確定因素，導致2025年下半年的集裝箱需求疲弱，因大部分傳統上第3季出口貨量需求已提前集中於2025年上半年付運。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15588017-%e5%8b%9d%e7%8d%85%e8%b2%a8%e6%ab%83%e7%99%bc%e7%9b%88%e8%ad%a6-%e6%96%99%e5%8e%bb%e5%b9%b4%e7%b4%94%e5%88%a9%e8%b7%8c%e6%9c%80%e5%b0%9147",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240717_FI_source-web_00716.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-16 16:50:30",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "永嘉旗下高級時裝零售業務上季同店銷售升2%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">永嘉集團(03322)公布，旗下高級時裝零售業務上季直營實體店舖同店銷售增長2%，2025年全年則跌4%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"永嘉官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/570x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/03322_web_1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"永嘉官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/570x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/03322_web_1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">永嘉官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">以區域劃分，上季內地同店銷售升5%，全年跌2%；香港及澳門上季跌3%，全年跌13%；其他地區上季跌22%，全年跌11%。截至去年底，該公司直營實體店舖總數75間，按年淨減少27間。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">若以整體收益計，上述業務上季增長約16%，2025年全年亦升8%，主要由銷售予該品牌特許經營方的批發收益所帶動。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15587997-%e6%b0%b8%e5%98%89%e6%97%97%e4%b8%8b%e9%ab%98%e7%b4%9a%e6%99%82%e8%a3%9d%e9%9b%b6%e5%94%ae%e6%a5%ad%e5%8b%99%e4%b8%8a%e5%ad%a3%e5%90%8c%e5%ba%97%e9%8a%b7%e5%94%ae%e5%8d%872",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/03322-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-16 16:45:33",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "全日收市︱午後尋底 恒指跌78點報26844點 連續4日兩萬七得復失 單周累計仍升613點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股未能打破連續4日於兩萬七關口得而復失的魔咒，今午進一步尋底，但整周計依然回復升市，主板全日成交亦降至2550.79億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：港交所官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250203_FI_source-web_00388-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：港交所官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250203_FI_source-web_00388-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：港交所官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數今早跟隨外圍高開，於競價時段已重越27000點，以27094點開市，開市未幾升幅擴大至252點，衝上見27176點卻無以為繼，隨即迅速回落並於上午約10時再新轉跌失守27000點，開始反覆向下之路，午市後段見全日低位26741點、跌182點，尾市跌幅收窄。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指最後收報26844點，跌78點或0.29%；單周累計仍升613點或2.34%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數今日跌6點或0.11%，報5822點，單周累計也升135點或2.37%。國企指數今日跌46點或0.5%，報9220點，單周則升172點或1.9%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15587954-%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e5%b0%8b%e5%ba%95-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c78%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b126844%e9%bb%9e-%e9%80%a3%e7%ba%8c4%e6%97%a5%e5%85%a9%e8%90%ac%e4%b8%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-5.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-16 16:20:29",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "跌勢略擴 滬指收跌10點 深指跌0.18% 芯片及半導體相關股強勢未改",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地A股午後持續反覆，滬深兩市跌勢略為擴大，交投回升至3.03萬億元(人民幣‧下同)，芯片與半導體相關股則普遍逆市持續強勢。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中芯官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240509_FI_source-web_00981-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240509_FI_source-web_00981-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中芯官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指今早高開14點並於初段再上層樓，一度將升幅擴大至27點，高見4140點，在多番試高卻未能突破之下終於掉頭，於上午約10時開始倒跌，展開好淡爭持繼而反覆偏軟走勢，午市終失守4100點關口，最低報4091點，跌20點；滬指最後收報4101點，跌10點或0.26%，成交1.34萬億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指亦呈好淡爭持，今早高開67點後升幅最多擴大至117點，於初段做出全日高位14424點，其後反覆回吐，於上午10時過後一直呈好淡爭持，在13800點上下不足百點波動，低位14257點時亦只跌49點；深指收報14281點，跌25點或0.18%，成交1.69萬億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數跌19點或0.41%，以4731點收市；創業板指數跌6點或0.2%，報3361點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">單周計算，滬指跌0.45%，深指明顯跑贏，升1.14%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-8.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-8.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">台積電昨天公布的上季業績勝預期，利好芯片與半導體相關股氣氛。天岳先進(02631)A股(600234.SH)急飆，早於上午臨收市前升近20%封板，報111.19元；兆易創新(03986)A股(603986.SH)午後也加入漲停板行列，升約10%，收報280.46元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">峰岹科技(01304)A股(688279.SH)升幅則略為收窄至8.11%，報220元。相反，華虹(01347)A股(688347.SH)午後搶上，收漲6.87%，報140元；中芯國際(00981)A股(688981.SH)也升2.05%，報126.99元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"華虹 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250507_FI_source-ap_01347.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"華虹 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250507_FI_source-ap_01347.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">華虹 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">市場對美國向伊朗採取軍事行動憂慮緩和，國際油價昨天跌逾4%，「三桶油」A股今日全線向下。中國海油(00883)A股(600938.SH)跌2.36%，報29.33元；中國石化(00386)A股(600028.SH)跌1.85%，報5.84元；中國石油(00857)A股(601857.SH)亦跌1.71%，報9.8元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15587695-%e8%b7%8c%e5%8b%a2%e7%95%a5%e6%93%b4-%e6%bb%ac%e6%8c%87%e6%94%b6%e8%b7%8c10%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b7%b1%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c0-18-%e8%8a%af%e7%89%87%e5%8f%8a%e5%8d%8a%e5%b0%8e%e9%ab%94%e7%9b%b8%e9%97%9c%e8%82%a1",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_China-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-16 15:15:34",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        }
    ]
